<div>
<p class="font-label-caps text-on-surface mb-2">Spark AI Fluency</p>
<p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant">© 2024 Spark AI Fluency. Empowering the next generation.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-md md:justify-end">
<a class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary-container transition-colors" href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
